  ('judicial-f0899a01-moex-00486', 'judicial-f0899a01', 'judicial-f0899a01-moex-110-9a3b44c4', 'sub-judicial-f0899a01-01', NULL, 'essay', '刑事訴訟法第 8章之 1為「限制出境、出海」專章，其可分為逕行限制
